OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773349950
OL,3,C'Unsustainable' - Business owners plan
OL,4,Cto boycott payment in Carlisle
OL,6,FSome business owners in Carlisle have
OL,7,Fsaid they will boycott payments that
OL,8,Fcontribute to maintaining and
OL,9,Fpromoting part of the city.
OL,11,FBusinesses operating in the Business
OL,12,FImprovement District (BID) have to pay
OL,13,Fan annual fee.
OL,15,FBut Lynn Steadman from Aztec Adventure
OL,16,FPlay is one of those who believe that
OL,17,Fthe payments are becoming
OL,18,Funsustainable as various other costs
OL,19,Frise.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773349950
OL,3,C'Unsustainable' - Business owners plan
OL,4,Cto boycott payment in Carlisle
OL,6,FThe BID scheme has been introduced so
OL,7,Fthat firms within a designated area of
OL,8,Fthe city agree to invest collectively
OL,9,Fin projects and services to improve
OL,10,Ftheir trading environment.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV Border, Lynn Steadman
OL,13,Fsaid: "We are really struggling as it
OL,14,Fis.
OL,16,F"We are going to lose our relief at
OL,17,Fthe end of March so we will be paying
OL,18,Ffull business rates which is going to
OL,19,Fbe a huge extra payment.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773349950
OL,3,C'Unsustainable' - Business owners plan
OL,4,Cto boycott payment in Carlisle
OL,6,F"Also the minimum wage is going up and
OL,7,Fthen putting another increase on us on
OL,8,Ftop of everything else is
OL,9,Funsustainable."
OL,11,FLynn shared plans that she and other
OL,12,Flocal business owners in the city now
OL,13,Fplan to withhold payments to the BID.
OL,15,FShe said: "I am willing to make a
OL,16,Fstand and we feel like if everyone
OL,17,Fcomes together as one big community we
OL,18,Fare going to be stronger."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773349950
OL,3,C'Unsustainable' - Business owners plan
OL,4,Cto boycott payment in Carlisle
OL,6,FChristopher Scott from Border City
OL,7,FAutos shared his views on the
OL,8,Fsituation.
OL,10,FHe said: "I don't believe it was
OL,11,Fexplained properly and I don't believe
OL,12,Fwe were given the right consultation.
OL,14,F"The information that was given was
OL,15,Fprobably not as factually correct as
OL,16,Fwhat we should have been given.
OL,18,F"I think more information should have
OL,19,Fbeen given to those businesses who
OL,20,Fwere compulsory told to pay the BID."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
