CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773349950
OL,3,C'Unsustainable' - Business owners plan
OL,4,Cto boycott payment in Carlisle
OL,6,FThe Great Border City BID team said in
OL,7,Fa statement: "The Great Border City
OL,8,FBID was approved through a formal
OL,9,Fballot of eligible businesses late
OL,10,Flast year.
OL,12,F"The levy is collected by Cumberland
OL,13,FCouncil under the national regulations
OL,14,Fthat govern Business Improvement
OL,15,FDistricts.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773349950
OL,3,C'Unsustainable' - Business owners plan
OL,4,Cto boycott payment in Carlisle
OL,6,F"The BID is currently being set up,
OL,7,Fwith a Board now in place and work
OL,8,Funderway to develop a programme of
OL,9,Factivity including events, promotion
OL,10,Fof Carlisle and engagement with
OL,11,Fbusinesses across the city.
OL,13,F"These are still the early stages of
OL,14,Festablishing the BID, and the focus at
OL,15,Fpresent is on putting the organisation
OL,16,Fand its programme in place so
OL,17,Fbusinesses can begin to see the
OL,18,Fbenefits.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773349950
OL,3,C'Unsustainable' - Business owners plan
OL,4,Cto boycott payment in Carlisle
OL,6,F"As with any ballot process there will
OL,7,Fbe a range of views, and the BID
OL,8,Fremains open to constructive
OL,9,Fengagement with businesses as the
OL,10,Fprogramme develops."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
